              "left_image_with_text_copy": "Colorist Johnny Ramirez is responsible for some of the most beautiful blondes in Los Angeles. He's known for his soft, natural, sun-kissed looks---what he calls \"lived-in color\". Here are his top tips for living with salon-born blonde.\n<br><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/blogs/product-spotlight/the-faux-blonde-s-survival-guide\">Read More</a>"
            }
